>Description:
On installing the x64-Version of Racket on Windows 7 64-bit, the default directory which is used is "C:Program Files (x86)"

This is okay for the x86-Version of Racket, but in general, x64-programs should choose the Directory "C:Program Files" on a 64-bit Operating System.
